StmtSimple.StatementText: SELECT city.id AS id, city.name + ', ' + country_division.name + ', ' + country.name AS display_name, ranking, population, density FROM city INNER JOIN country ON city.iso3 = country.iso3 INNER JOIN country_division ON city.division_id = country_division.id WHERE show_division = 1 AND country_division.name IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT city.id AS id, city.name + ', ' + country.name AS display_name,ranking,population,density FROM city INNER JOIN country ON city.iso3 = country.iso3 WHERE show_division = 1 AND city.division_id IS NULL UNION SELECT city.id AS id, city.name + ', ' + country.name AS display_name,ranking,population,density FROM city INNER JOIN country ON city.iso3 = country.iso3 WHERE show_division IS NULL OR show_division = 0
